<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She went public with her boyfriend comedian Jack Whitehall in April.</p>

<p>But Roxy Horner enjoyed a night on the town with friends at MNKY HSE restaurant in Mayfair on Thursday night.</p>

<p>The model, 29, exuded glamour in a cream silk crop top and white flared trousers as she left the swanky London eatery. </p>

<p>Gorgeous: Jack Whitehall's girlfriend Roxy Horner exuded glamour in a cream silk crop top and white flared trousers for a night out in London on Thursday night</p>

<p>She teamed the going-out look with white cross-bar heels and a gold handbag as she stepped out with friends.  </p>

<p>Roxy wore her blonde tresses in a chic top knot and opted for a natural makeup look with a slick of pink lip. </p>

<p>The beauty kept her accessories to a minimum but carried a black face mask and phone in her hand.   </p>

<p>Glowing: She teamed the going-out look with white cross-bar heels and a gold handbag as she stepped out with friends</p>

<p>Gorgeous: Roxy wore her blonde tresses in a chic top knot and opted for a natural makeup look with a slick of pink lip</p>

<p>Roxy and Jack are said to have made their romance exclusive just before the UK-wide coronavirus lockdown.</p>

<p>The comedian shared his first Instagram post with the model and even posted a funny video of her giving him a quarantine haircut earlier this year. </p>

<p>A source told The Sun at the time: 'Jack and Roxy are enjoying being in isolation together. It's all very new but they're in their own little bubble and things are perfect at the moment. </p>

<p>Chic: The beauty kept her accessories to a minimum and but carried a black face mask and phone in her hand</p>

<p>Model behaviour: Roxy looked in high spirits as she left the bar on Thursday night after meeting a group of friends</p>

<p>'Being on lockdown in a honeymoon period is certainly one way to get to know each other quickly. But the more time they spend together the happier they seem.  </p>

<p>'Both have had their share of heartbreak and struggled a bit to find love. It's time they had some luck.'  </p>

<p>Roxy has a string of famous exes, having previously been linked to A-list actor Leonardo DiCaprio and singer Jake Bugg who she split from in December.</p>

<p>Jack has been linked to various women since calling it quits with actress Gemma Chan, 37, in December 2017 after six years together. She is now in a relationship with screen star Dominic Cooper.</p>

